               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary, ቅዳሴ" ማርያም", Canticle of the Flower, ማሕሌተ፡ ጽጌ፡, Collection of Qene Poems</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="27v" facs="005">Fols 1r–27v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-qǝddus Hǝryāqos za-hagara Bǝhnǝsā</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="28v" to="72v" facs="033">Fols 28v–72v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1834Mahlet">Māḫleta ṣǝge</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: እግዚአብሔር: ሕያው: በልሳነ: ኵሉ: ዘይትነገር: በስምኪ: ማርያም: ወላዲተ: ክቡር። ማኅሌተ: ጽጌኪ: ወጠንኩ: ለተአምርኪ: መዝሙር። ማርያም: ድንግል: ንግሥተ: ሰማይ: ወምድር። አምጣነ: ይጥዕም: ውዳሴኪ: እመዓር: ወሦከር።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="74r" to="78v" facs="078">Fols 74r–78v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>chapters 17, 16, and 8</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="79r" to="81v" facs="083">Fols 79r–81v</locus><title>Collection of Qǝnǝ Poems</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ፃማ: ኢኮነ: ለሐራ: ድንግል: ፃማሁ። እስመ: በብርሃን: ፈጸመ: ግብረ: አስተብርኮ: ለሊሁ።</incipit>
                </msItem>
